U7 chit8 e5 lang5 ti7 hiong-chhoan be5 lou7, chiu7 mng7 chit8 e5 ta-pou gin2-na2 kong2, “ChhiaN2 mng7 siaN5-chhi7 ti7 ta2-loh8?”  
Hit e5 gin2-na2 in3 kong2, “SiaN5-chhi7?  Goa2 m7 bat khi3, goa2 m7 chai, chong2-si7 goa2 chai ti7 soaN nih hit peng5, thang tui3 chit tiau5 lou7 tit8-tit8 khi3 chiu7 oe7 kau3.”  
Hit e5 lang5 ka7 i soeh-sia7 liau2-au7 chiu7 ng3 gin2-na2 sou2 kong2 e5 hong-hiong3 khi3, ko2-jian5 kau3 bok8-tek-te7.
Ia5-sou kong2, “Goa2 si7 lou7..., ti7 Goa2 Pe7 e5 ke u7 choe7-choe7 chhu3-theh8.”  Thian-tong5 ti7 ta2-loh8? Lan2 na7 sin3 Ia5-sou, toe3 I chiu7 e7 kau3 ui7.
(“Ki5-biau7 e5 Ia5-sou”, Iah8 100-102 )
</CL>
